==English==

===Noun===
{{infl|en|noun|head=[[merry]] [[Christmas]]}}

# Used to express good wishes at Christmas time.
#: '''''Merry Christmas''', Jack.'' / ''Same to you. And a happy New Year.''
#: ''Have a '''merry Christmas''', Jack.'' / '''''Merry Christmas''' to you and your family.''

